    "body": "## Summary\r\n- Fix KV cache scale handling in compressed-tensors quantization\r\n- Ensures `_k_scale_float` and `_v_scale_float` are properly set for KV cache quantization\r\n\r\nFlashinfer uses both `_k_scale` and `_k_scale_float`:\r\nhttps://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/blob/6c749399b7dc939a592e30d5964d7bdf255427aa/vllm/v1/attention/backends/flashinfer.py#L1510\r\nhttps://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/blob/6c749399b7dc939a592e30d5964d7bdf255427aa/vllm/v1/attention/backends/flashinfer.py#L1318\r\n\r\n\r\n## Test plan\r\n\r\nTested with [Qwen3-8B-MXFP4-FP8KV](https://huggingface.co/Yi30/Qwen3-8B-MXFP4-FP8KV) model:\r\n- Without fix: Garbled output like \"broadcast返回罨返回返回返回返回返回返回的同时arya稳定有价值当之无愧无限稳\"\r\n- With fix: Correct output like \"Kaitlyn. I am a 21 year old woman who is a\"",
